query:
SELECT 
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tools) as total_tools,
    (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT name) FROM tools) as unique_tools,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tools) - (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT name) FROM tools) as duplicate_count;
